# =====================
# CREDIT SYSTEM APIs
# =====================

### Get Credit Balance (Protected)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/credits/balance
Authorization: Bearer <YOUR_TOKEN>

### Get User Transactions with Pagination (Protected)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/credits/transactions?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer <YOUR_TOKEN>

### Get User Transactions filtered by type (Protected)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/credits/transactions?type=meal_purchase&page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer <YOUR_TOKEN>

### Add Credits to User (Admin Only)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/credits/add
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_TOKEN>

{
  "userId": "<USER_ID>",
  "amount": 500,
  "description": "Monthly credits allocation"
}

### Get All Transactions with Pagination (Admin Only)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/credits/all-transactions?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_TOKEN>

### Get All Transactions filtered by userId (Admin Only)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/credits/all-transactions?userId=<USER_ID>&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_TOKEN>

# =====================
# MENU SYSTEM APIs
# =====================

### Get All Menu Items with Pagination (Public)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/menu?page=1&limit=10

### Get Breakfast Menu with Pagination (Public)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/menu?category=breakfast&page=1&limit=10

### Get Available Menu Items sorted by price (Public)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/menu?available=true&sort=-price&page=1&limit=10

### Get Single Menu Item (Public)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/menu/<MEAL_ID>

### Create Menu Item (Admin Only)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/menu
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_TOKEN>

{
  "mealName": "Idli Sambar",
  "price": 30,
  "category": "breakfast",
  "description": "2 Idlis with sambar and chutney",
  "available": true
}

### Create Another Menu Item (Admin Only)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/menu
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_TOKEN>

{
  "mealName": "Veg Thali",
  "price": 60,
  "category": "lunch",
  "description": "Rice, dal, sabzi, roti, salad",
  "available": true
}

### Update Menu Item (Admin Only)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/menu/<MEAL_ID>
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_TOKEN>

{
  "price": 35,
  "description": "3 Idlis with sambar and chutney"
}

### Toggle Meal Availability (Admin Only)
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/menu/<MEAL_ID>/availability
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_TOKEN>

### Delete Menu Item (Admin Only)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/menu/<MEAL_ID>
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_TOKEN>

# =====================
# MEAL PURCHASE APIs
# =====================

### Purchase Meal (Protected)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/menu/<MEAL_ID>/purchase
Authorization: Bearer <YOUR_TOKEN>